Properties.Name: InstructionalText
Properties.Value: The AMC Banking 365 Fundamentals extension saves you time and reduces errors when you send data to your bank. The extension uses the AMC Banking 365 Business service to transform data from Microsoft Dynamics 365 Business Central into formats that banks require. You specify the bank, and the extension does the rest. For more information, see the documentation.
